Description: Papyrus fragment bearing 6 lines of a Coptic text written against the fibres (verso) and 1 line along the fibres (recto). EA 75390, 75391, 75392, 75393, 75394, 75395 are mounted together.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380716) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380716)
